title: Crenshaw Announces November Mobile Office Hours for Baker County (Ander Crenshaw)
text: ( Source : Ander Crenshaw ) Crenshaw Announces November Mobile Office Hours for Baker County WASHINGTON, DC - Congressman Ander Crenshaw announced Fourth Congressional District mobile office hours for Baker County for the month of November.
